quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,113,"Yahuud en mbi'i nasaara en ngonaani he hay huunde nasaara en mbii yahuud en ngonaani he hay huunde, tawa e…ìe njannga deftere nde, ko hono ngol konngol …ìe nganndaa …ìee mbi'noo ko Alla √±aawata luural hakkunde ma…ì…ìe √±ande darnga."
  2,114,"Hombo …ìuri too√±de oon ka…óoowo yoo innde Alla jante nder juulir…óe ombo daranii bonnude …óe , …ìeen potaani naatde …óe so wonaa e kulol, …ìe ke…ìa koyeera e aduna …ìe ke…ìa lette maw…óe to laakara."
  2,115,"Fu…ónaange e hirnaange ko Alla woodani kala heen …óo kuccit-…óon, toon ko yeeso Alla, pellet Alla noon ko jaaj…óo e ganngal Makko piiltingal."
  2,116,"∆Åe mbi'i Alla mo jogitii …ìi…ó…óo senaande woodanii mo, nganndee kala ko woni e asamaanji e lesdi ko Kanko woodani fof na …óoftoo mo."
  2,117,"Pu…ó…óu…óo asamaanji (ndowguuji ) …óii e lesdi ndi, so o √±aawii huunde o wi'ata …óum tan ko: won …óum wona."
  2,118,"∆Åe nganndaa …ìee mbi'a mate Alla haaldataa he min wolla o addana min maande, ko noon adinoo…ìe ma…ì…ìe mbi'noo …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe nanndii , goonga tigi min la…ì…ìinii maandeeji …óii wonande yim…ìe yananaa…ìe …ìee ."
  2,119,"Minen min nelirii ma goonga ngonaa beltinoowo jeertinoowo, a naamnetaake yim…ìe jayngol Jahannama."